{"tid":1890364,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[黃色youtuber圈]發覺一字馬真係比人低估左","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T04:33:42.000Z","uid":67294,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb677ffed8141880ed9067c4bb0f65d4cacec1de","tid":1890364,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"有無人仲記得一字馬?<br />\n依家發覺佢地啲idea真係行得好前<br />\n<br />\n例如第一條片, 5年前己經玩扮藍絲反入侵, 又有創意(改歐聯主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ljqpKVczDU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DljqpKVczDU4&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=8189c71f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ljqpKVczDU4</a><br />\n梁天琦時代己經拍光復上水既片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6TyHNSLdQ7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6TyHNSLdQ7w&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=3768c654\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6TyHNSLdQ7w</a><br />\n紅左之後己經即時轉拍支持小店, 同依家黃色經濟圈差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EC1gFKJYQYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEC1gFKJYQYc&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=30a06715\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EC1gFKJYQYc</a><br />\n<br />\n仲要政治立場鮮明, 唔會有咩兩個黃一個藍都當黃咁既理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人知佢地去哂邊? 會唔會變左奶共藍絲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95078537bf9252b28205d5570a7ff00471dfdbd7","tid":1890364,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"一字馬好似係CU學生會校園電台既莊員組成，畢左業之後就散左了。"},{"pid":"2bb0c33887b4139a